attributes.title: No❤️
attributes.review:
I firstly download this app to show my support to the amazing bunker boy😳oops i meant president. Anyways after 365 days of trying to download the app it finally did and may i add that i always have VERY good internet and the app itself was the problem. Once i opened the app an old, saggy, crusty, musty, dusty, absolutely revolting and disgusting orange 🍊 appeared on my screen. I spent months crying and wondering what i did to deserve that. Once i took hold of myself i looked at the phone once again and suddenly my eyes started burning and everything was orange. I threw my phone to the side and the WORST THING HAPPENED... the orange CAME OUT OF THE SCREEN i was absolutely mortified. He then started walking 🚶‍♀️ towards me covered in trump merch screaming at the top of his lungs TRUMP 2020!!!! As i was about to slap him he hid in the bunker with all the lights off...i immediately went to delete the app but it had left a virus 🦠 on my phone😪i threw the phone away and went to buy a new one while i was setting it up the oompa loompa came out of the bunker 😔AND BROKE MY NEW PHONE BECAUSE IT DIDNT HAVE THE TRUMP APP😡🤬😠i was so sad 😞 but then willy wonka came out of the closet and told his oompa loompa to stop and get back to work. He gave me a new phone 📱 and apologized for the orange giving me a bad time he also offered me free candy for the rest of my life. I accepted and had a little “chat” with bunker boy i proceeded to kick and punch him while willy was holding my hoops (thx willy). So yes that was basically my experience with the app so i suggest ya’ll dont get it because the same thing will happen to you. Girl honestly to this day i still get nightmares. I lost the best years of my life to this app😭so i DEFINITELY think the app should be deleted immediately. Love all of you (unless you’re the orange 🍊 if you are then yo mama made a mistake sweetie pie🧚🏻💕🥰😘😍🥺) u tried🥺❤️🧚🏻🥰😍now never try again🧚🏻💕☀️🥰🥺 and as for ur mother i am genuinely sorry u had to wait and suffer nine months to find out u were having an orange😪so sad...anyways thx for the attention as to why this app is so terrible buh-bye now❤️

                                                   Yours truly, 
                                                     Willys wife😘
